Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, python3, python3-kpyutils, python3-yaml, python3-dateparser, python3-tabulate, python3-natsort, zfsutils-linux, cryptsetup, udev, systemd
Description: event-driven ZFS mirror backup manager daemon
 zmirror is a Python CLI and daemon for managing ZFS mirror backup devices,
 including LUKS/dm-crypt backed devices.
 .
 It reacts to udev and ZFS events, tracks pool/device state, and can run
 maintenance operations such as scrub/trim/resilver on schedule.
